{"tid":184071,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係YYLAM, 你會繼續教書另炒樓/股?另直接退休","createTime":"2017-04-02T14:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T06:43:46.000Z","uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0d35bef4506846822c6890cf93c514dafdbe4f","tid":184071,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"YYLAM紅左已經係幾年前既事, 第二屆DSE佢已經稱霸<br />\n到2015年, 間野搞上市, 踢爆左佢頂住半間遵理, 果時仲傳年薪8000萬<br />\n其實我唔明點解佢仲要打工, 一個普通香港仔, 四,五百萬(假設有層供斷左既自住樓), 已經夠你慢慢MEET過世<br />\n佢而家已經有幾層物業係手, 其實真係冇咩必要繼續咁CHUR自己<br />\n每個月又要整筆記, 又要教訂, 又要通頂捱壞自己, 又要整MOCK等等<br />\n點解唔直接炒樓好過?"},{"pid":"ec9c0cab7507320f18b121ca03eba613fedae5dc","tid":184071,"uid":41742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"播下video有幾千萬都唔做？"},{"pid":"23449ad49dfddd1b755f422ee1043232478f965c","tid":184071,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"有啲人做野唔係為錢"},{"pid":"819b442a6e6aaf5828e0eb2f642eda4cd57b8b02","tid":184071,"uid":52004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"收租冇學生妹食<br />\n<br />\n又或者佢真係好鐘意教中文"},{"pid":"8a24bdbb22fd4bf4c70b03500a6d8dcc9c89b0e4","tid":184071,"uid":1205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"另夠未"},{"pid":"83cc72912dced2f9d802d5b8a9f238789fa6706e","tid":184071,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>播下video有幾千萬都唔做？</blockquote><br />\n..."},{"pid":"6d99191bd1e41a94c39dbab52c3ebe79d0265c50","tid":184071,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲人做野唔係為錢</blockquote><br />\n你講野咁好笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c56167f35c541cc